show.description: Panathai semikka pala vazhigal irukku, aana edhu nammaloda vaazhviyalukku porundhum nu yosichu thittamidanum. Ovvuru panam saarndha thittagal pathina vilakkam, athnoda payangal enna nu indha book oda author namakka kuduthurukkaru, adhu mattum illa neriya money saving  tips indha book la ungalukku iruku so miss pannama full ah kelunga
